<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HALLELUJAH, MAW KA KHAMHTU CH462</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pathian Fa a rungtum ah, &quot;Ngaih-chiatnak tuarmi,&quot; an ti, Cucu
 khua-ruahhar a si, Hal-le-lu-jah, Maw ka Khamhtu!

[V2]
 Ningzah le nihsawh tuar in, Kei ca sualphawt in a dir, Thi in ka sual
 a ngaihthiam, Hal-le-lu-jah, Maw ka Khamhtu!

[V3]
 Pathian Tuufa thiang a si, Kannih cu misual kan si, Remnak a si kho
 hnga maw? Hal-le-lu-jah, Maw ka Khamhtu!

[V4]
 Thah awkah Jesuh an tar, &quot;A dih cang,&quot; tiin a au, Van ah thangthat in
 a um, Hal-le-lu-jah, maw ka Khamhtu!

[V5]
 Kan Bawi sungbik rat tikah, Tlanhmi van in auh awkah, Hi hla kan sa
 than te lai, Hal-le-lu-jah, maw ka Khamhtu!</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<hymn_number>462</hymn_number>
</song>